  <p>Declares a new <link xref="Cogl.IndexBuffer"/> of @size bytes to contain vertex
indices. Once declared, data can be set using
<link xref="Cogl.buffer_set_data"/> or by mapping it into the application's
address space using <link xref="Cogl.buffer_map"/>.</p>
